{"id":299087,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/美国之音-南非人民祝愿曼德拉早日康复/","date":"2013-06-14T17:18:07Z","modified":"2013-06-14T17:18:07Z","title":"美国之音 | 南非人民祝愿曼德拉早日康复","content":"<p><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/9072A644-471F-4861-8ED9-512EECB1309F_w640_r1_s.jpg\" /></p>\n<div>星期五 学童唱歌,祝愿曼德拉早日康复. 曼德拉由于肺部感染仍然住院疗养.</p>\n<p>这群儿童，携带气球和海报，聚集在比勒陀利亚医院外。现年94岁的南非前总统过去七天以来，就住在这家医院.</p>\n<p>南非现任总统雅各布•祖马周四晚去医院探望了曼德拉先生。探访结束后，南非领导人说, 曼德拉先生病况持续改善，但他的病情依然严重。</p>\n<p>他要求人们继续为曼德拉祈祷<br />自去年12月以来,这是这位反种族隔离的代表人物第四次因肺部感染住院。</div>\n<p><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/6600D78F-6324-42D2-AF97-D3DFABB51CD6_w308.jpg\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http/www.voachinese.com/content/south-africa-mandela-20130614/1681960.html\" /></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":998,"categories":[18270,18269,8779],"tags":[19866,12012,9593]}